  "texts": [
    "Emergency Response",
    "The IAEA establishes and maintains an international response system for nuclear accidents and radiological emergencies, supporting rapid and effective responses in the event of an accident. 5",
    "Nuclear Material Management",
    "The IAEA operates a system to monitor and verify the use, storage, and transportation of nuclear materials.",
    "This system ensures that nuclear materials are used solely for peaceful purposes and plays a crucial role in preventing nuclear proliferation. 6"
  ]
}